claim.claim-text:
The information interaction method according to claim 1, wherein the interaction item comprises:
an interaction item for inputting and/or displaying knowledge;
an interaction item for inputting and/or displaying question and answer information;
an interaction item for inputting and/or displaying contact means;
an interaction item for inputting and/or displaying a contact person;
an interaction item for inputting and/or displaying a contact time;
an interaction item for inputting and/or displaying a contact address; and/or
an interaction item for displaying a second video.

The information interaction method according to claim 1, wherein the first predetermined condition comprises one or more of:
the first video is played for a first predetermined period of time;
the first video is played to a first predetermined video frame of the first video;
the first video is played to a first predetermined time instant of the first video; and
the first video is repeatedly played for a first repetition number of times.

The information interaction method according to claim 1, wherein the second predetermined condition comprises one or more of:
the first video is played for a second predetermined period of time;
the first video is played to a second predetermined video frame of the first video;
the first video is played to a second predetermined time instant of the first video; and
the first video is repeatedly played for a second repetition number of times.
